          </svg>
          Emergency Hotline
        </a>
        <a href="https://wa.me/971XXXXXXXXX?text=EMERGENCY" target="_blank" class="bg-orange-500 text-white font-bold py-4 px-8 rounded-xl hover:bg-orange-600 transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
