          </svg>
          Emergency WhatsApp
        </a>
      </div>
      <p class="text-red-200 text-sm mt-4">
        Average response time: Within 1 hour across Dubai
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Final CTA -->
    <div class="text-center mt-16">
      <p class="text-2xl text-primary-100 mb-6">
        🏠 <strong>Welcome to Dubai!</strong> Let us help you settle in perfectly. 🏠
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 text-sm text-primary-200">
        <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
